scons: an Open Source software construction tool
scons:
scons: 
scons: SCons is a software construction tool--that is, a superior
scons: alternative to the classic "Make" build tool that we all know
scons: and love.
scons: 
scons: SCons is implemented as a Python script and set of modules, and SCons
scons: "configuration files" are actually executed as Python scripts. This
scons: gives SCons many powerful capabilities not found in other software
scons: build tools.
scons:
